getModelNames

public java.util.Set<java.lang.String> getModelNames()
Specified by:
getModelNames in interface IModelStructure
Returns:
The names of all the models managed by this structure. To each model is associated an independent collection of tree hierarchies of IModelObjects identified by the name of the model it maps.
